            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Amalcari">Amolcari</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Warnicausus">Warnicausi</name></persName> quia
                        per hanc paginam decerno ut dum ego advivere meruero, quod subter aliquid de
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> mea iudicavero in mea sit
                        potestate de ea faciendi quod voluero. Et si <persName key="#Freedman"><name
                                ref="Sintruda">Sindruda</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freedman">obsequiale</rs> mea super decessu meo vixerit, volo ut
                        parte de <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> mea, mea portione tras <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >flumen</rs> in loco <placeName key="#Rivers #Wine" ref="#places/633"
                            >Isclito</placeName> in integrum; simul et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs> mea in <placeName key="#Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/421">Arena</placeName>, mea portione in integrum; et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> mea in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/1000">Antuniano</placeName>, mea
                        portione in integrum; hec omnia, post meo decessu, sit in potestate ipsius
                        Sindrude usufructuando et regendo tantum. Post vero meo decessu si iterum a
                        me suprascriptas res iniudicata remanserit et post decessu ipsius Sindrude,
                        omnia sit in potestate <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/294">Sancti
                            Donati</orgName>, ubi <persName key="#Archdeacons"><name
                                ref="Ragibertus">Rachipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archdeacons">archidiaconus</rs> rector esse videtur, et in <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/246">Sancti
                            Georgi</orgName>, ubi <persName><name ref="Frosinus"
                            >Frosinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> rector esse videtur. <foreign>Se qualcuno
                            dei parenti contestasse queste disposizioni, pena in duplum.</foreign>
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Amolcari; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Irnicausus">Irnicausi</name></persName>
                                germano eius testis; <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Liliodari"
                            >Lilioderi</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Alpari"
                                >Alpari</name></persName> testis; + <persName  key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Warimbertus">Warniperti</name></persName> idem germano eius
                                testis. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Osprandus">Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
